---[ INSTALL ]---------------------------------------------------------------

OpenTelegard does not currently have a fully working environment. In order to
setup and use the current source code snapshot from the repository, you can
follow the steps outlined here.

 Prerequisites:
   - Preferred platform is "Linux-amd64"
   - Preferred IDE is NetBeans >= 6.7
   - Install a Java JRE >= 1.6
   - Install the JRuby Interpretter (http://jruby.org)
   - Install the following jruby gems:
       o  gem install   rails \
			haml \
		        activerecord-jdbcpostgresql-adapter \
			dojo-pkg \
			haml_scaffold \
			highline \
			jdbc-postgres \
		        rack \
			warbler      

